Awak dengarlah nasihat.

103
00:04:32,240 --> 00:04:33,319
Mak cik dah kelam-kabut.

104
00:04:34,840 --> 00:04:35,680
Saya tidak kisah.

105
00:04:35,920 --> 00:04:36,840
