192
00:07:59,280 --> 00:08:00,800
mesti berhati-hati

193
00:08:00,879 --> 00:08:02,120
supaya tidak melakukan kesilapan.

194
00:08:02,319 --> 00:08:03,639
Selain itu, kena membimbing
kakitangan junior

195
00:08:03,639 --> 00:08:05,160
dan mengaturkan kerja

196
00:08:05,160 --> 00:08:06,559
semasa cuti bersalin saya.

197
00:08:06,759 --> 00:08:07,600
Jika tidak

198
00:08:07,600 --> 00:08:08,680
diatur dengan baik,

199
00:08:08,720 --> 00:08:09,680
semasa tamatnya cuti bersalin,

200
00:08:09,680 --> 00:08:10,680
saya pun kehilangan kerja.

201
00:08:10,840 --> 00:08:11,800
Adakah begitu serius?

202
00:08:11,840 --> 00:08:12,920
Adakah awak ingat senang?

203
00:08:13,399 --> 00:08:14,160
Biarkan saya memberitahu awak.

204
00:08:14,160 --> 00:08:15,600
Tempat kerja sangat kejam.

205
00:08:15,879 --> 00:08:17,600
Kerja baik tidak semestinya
naik pangkat dan gaji.

206
00:08:17,600 --> 00:08:18,160
Namun, kalau kerja dengan tidak memuaskan,

207
00:08:18,160 --> 00:08:19,639
pasti akan dibuang kerja.

208
00:08:22,040 --> 00:08:23,160
Berlagak untuk mendapat simpati.

209
00:08:23,639 --> 00:08:25,439
Payahnya juga kami mengambil
peperiksaan sekolah menengah.

210
00:08:25,879 --> 00:08:26,680
Jadi,

211
00:08:26,840 --> 00:08:28,319
mari kita bekerja keras bersama-sama.

212
00:08:28,399 --> 00:08:28,999
Betul?

213
00:08:29,280 --> 00:08:30,959
Mari kita tetapkan jadual waktu.

214
00:08:31,079 --> 00:08:32,639
Kemudian, berusaha mengikut jadual.

215
00:08:32,800 --> 00:08:34,079
Awak bekerja keras untuk mengambil
peperiksaan sekolah menengah.

216
00:08:34,120 --> 00:08:35,399
Ibu bekerja keras untuk
melahirkan anak kedua.

217
00:08:35,720 --> 00:08:36,959
Bukankah hanya setengah tahun?

218
00:08:37,399 --> 00:08:38,959
Kita bekerja keras, semua akan
berlalu dengan cepat.

219
00:08:42,799 --> 00:08:43,519
Ibu.

220
00:08:44,799 --> 00:08:45,639
Saya rasa

221
00:08:45,720 --> 00:08:46,399
kesayangan ayah

222
00:08:46,399 --> 00:08:48,200
pada saya berkurangan.

223
00:08:49,799 --> 00:08:50,759
