224
00:08:50,759 --> 00:08:51,759
Anak saya.

225
00:08:52,399 --> 00:08:53,080
Ini tidak mungkin.

226
00:08:55,639 --> 00:08:56,560
Sebenarnya,

227
00:08:56,919 --> 00:08:58,720
saya masih belum menerima sepenuhnya

228
00:08:58,960 --> 00:09:01,200
hakikat kelahiran adik.

229
00:09:01,639 --> 00:09:03,279
Mungkin seketika sebelum ini,

230
00:09:03,399 --> 00:09:04,440
datuk jatuh sakit,

231
00:09:04,600 --> 00:09:05,759
mak su mengalami kelahiran pramatang,

232
00:09:05,759 --> 00:09:06,960
awak pula menstabilkan janin,

233
00:09:07,879 --> 00:09:10,039
saya rasa saya terpaksa menjadi matang.

