00:09:11,759 --> 00:09:12,600
Kasihan.

235
00:09:12,720 --> 00:09:13,399
Anak saya.

236
00:09:14,279 --> 00:09:14,720
Sayang.

237
00:09:14,919 --> 00:09:15,320
Ya.

238
00:09:15,320 --> 00:09:16,960
Sila berikan pendirian awak segera.

239
00:09:17,200 --> 00:09:17,960
Anak perempuan kata,

240
00:09:17,960 --> 00:09:19,080
awak kurang sayang padanya.

241
00:09:19,999 --> 00:09:21,240
Tidak mungkin.

242
00:09:25,159 --> 00:09:26,999
Mustahilnya saya tak sayangkan awak.

243
00:09:28,039 --> 00:09:30,120
Awaklah anak perempuan saya, Yunjie.

244
00:09:30,399 --> 00:09:32,080
Ayah masih ingat lagi

245
00:09:32,639 --> 00:09:34,159
perasaan semasa memeluk awak
buat kali pertama.

246
00:09:34,999 --> 00:09:36,399
Ketika itu, awak baru saja dilahirkan.

247
00:09:37,279 --> 00:09:38,600
Jururawat menghulurkan awak kepada saya,

248
00:09:39,279 --> 00:09:40,840
memesan saya angkat lengan saya sedikit.

249
00:09:42,320 --> 00:09:43,039
Kepala awak yang kecil

